Create the Lambda function (Python 3.12)
A. Function

Lambda → Create function

Name: collegeHelpdeskHandler

Runtime: Python 3.12

Architecture: x86_64

Execution role: Create a new role with basic permissions

Create function

B. Environment variables (Configuration → Environment variables → Edit)

STUDENTS_TABLE = Students
FAQS_TABLE     = Faqs
C. Increase timeout
Configuration → General configuration → Edit → Timeout = 15 seconds → Save.

D. Paste code (Code tab → replace contents → Deploy)
(Check the .py file)
